  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Technical, financial and coordination support to address the education related UNICEF CCCs during disaster management to government and cluster members with emphasis on access to education services to the most vulnerable children and adolescents girls. \r\nSupport partners to scale up School Zone Of Peace initiative in  nine terai districts to ensure education rights of the  children in the most disadvantaged areas. \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nPre positioning of adequate emergency education supplies, distribution and management to restoration of learning during crisis.\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nTraining on DRR and Emergency Preparedness and response to develop capacity of national, regional and district partners with special focus on women and adolescents."
    },
    "ne": null
